CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 26, 1946, pg. 17 reads: "Magnet - While Louis was in Courier offices Tuesday he became the magnet for autograph seekers. He's calm as usual. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Joe Louis signing copies of book "Joe Louis American" for five women in room with Robert L. Vann image on back wall, in Pittsburgh Courier offices
